No. 9297. The Barr Cash & Package Carrier Company v. Auerbach et al. Error to Circuit Court of Richland county. *489Messrs. Jenner & Weldoh, for plaintiff in error. Messrs. Cummings, McBride & Wolfe and Messrs. Maguire & Galbraith, for defendants in error. Shauck, C. J., Price, Crew and Davis, JJ., concur.

(Decided May 1, 1906.)

• Judgment reversed and judgment for plaintiff in error.
